<p>(resource) singular-resources:</p>

<div class="language-txt highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>HTTP Verb     Path              Controller#Action   Used for
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>GET           /geocoder/new     geocoders#new       return an HTML form for creating the geocoder
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>POST          /geocoder         geocoders#create    create the new geocoder
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>GET           /geocoder         geocoders#show      display the one and only geocoder resource
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>GET           /geocoder/edit    geocoders#edit      return an HTML form for editing the geocoder
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>PATCH/PUT     /geocoder         geocoders#update    update the one and only geocoder resource
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>DELETE        /geocoder         geocoders#destroy   delete the geocoder resource
</pre></div>
</div>
