<p>(resources) crud-verbs-and-actions:</p>

<div class="language-txt highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>HTTP Verb     Path            Controller#Action   Used for
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n2" name="n2">2</a></span>GET           /photos         photos#index        display a list of all photos
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n3" name="n3">3</a></span>GET           /photos/new     photos#new          return an HTML form for creating a new photo
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n4" name="n4">4</a></span>POST          /photos         photos#create       create a new photo
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n5" name="n5">5</a></span>GET           /photos/:id     photos#show         display a specific photo
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n6" name="n6">6</a></span>GET           /photos/:id/edit  photos#edit       return an HTML form for editing a photo
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n7" name="n7">7</a></span>PATCH/PUT     /photos/:id     photos#update       update a specific photo
<span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n8" name="n8">8</a></span>DELETE        /photos/:id     photos#destroy      delete a specific photo
</pre></div>
</div>
